urlTitle
properties.DESCRIPTION: URL Title defines the string in a URL that Slatwall will use to identify this product.  For Example: http://www.myslatwallsite.com/sp/my-url-title/ where sp is the global product url key, and my-url-title is the urlTitle of this product

properties.NAME: productName
properties.DESCRIPTION: Defines the name of the product.  This can also be set at sku level with the skuName property.

properties.NAME: productCode
properties.DESCRIPTION: A unique value that identifies this product and only this product.  This could also be though of as a 'Model Number' but should not be confused with skuCode which identifies the actual unit being sold.

properties.NAME: productDescription
properties.DESCRIPTION: General marketing description of the product.

properties.NAME: publishedFlag
properties.DESCRIPTION: This flag is used to determine if the product should be available for sale as published on the frontend of a website.

properties.NAME: sortOrder
properties.DESCRIPTION: The sort order value can be used to manually organize all of the products in your catalog.

properties.NAME: purchaseStartDateTime
properties.DESCRIPTION: This field can be set to restrict the begining of a time periord when this product can be sold.

properties.NAME: purchaseEndDateTime
properties.DESCRIPTION: This field can be set to restrict the end of a time periord when this product can be sold.

properties.NAME: calculatedSalePrice
properties.DESCRIPTION: Stores the latest calculation of the dynamic 'salePrice' property which in turn calculates from the defaultSku's dynamic salePrice property.

properties.NAME: calculatedQATS
properties.DESCRIPTION: Stores the latest calculation of the dynamic 'qats' property which in turn calculates from the defaultSku's dynamic qats property.

properties.NAME: calculatedAllowBackorderFlag
properties.DESCRIPTION: Stores the value of the 'Allow Backorder' setting.  This is commonly used to drive dynamic product lists on the frontend where availability is important.
properties.DEPRECATEDDESCRIPTION: Because the calculatedQATS propert takes into account if a product is able to be backordered, this property is no longer needed and will be removed in a future release for performance reasons.

properties.NAME: calculatedTitle
properties.DESCRIPTION: Stores the latest calculation of the products marketing 'Title' which is generated based on a dynamic string template in the products settings.

properties.NAME: calculatedProductRating
properties.DESCRIPTION: Stores the latest calculation of the products Rating which is generated based on the average rating of productReviews.
